OL,3,CPrice of stamps blamed for Christmas
OL,4,Ccard decline
OL,6,FThe rising cost of stamps is being
OL,7,Fblamed for a fall in the number of
OL,8,FChristmas cards being sent by
OL,9,Fislanders this year.
OL,11,FAccording to Jersey Post, there's been
OL,12,Fa steady decline in the volume of
OL,13,FChristmas post passing through the
OL,14,Fservice since the pandemic.
OL,16,FWhilst 1 million items were sent in
OL,17,F2021, this year they expect to deliver
OL,18,Fjust over half of that - and
OL,19,Fanticipate a 10% year on year decline
OL,20,Fgoing forwards.
