OL,6,FCard sellers across both Channel
OL,7,FIslands argue that this decline is
OL,8,Fassociated with the price of stamps.
OL,10,FPip Heywood, managing director of
OL,11,FThortful greeting cards in Guernsey,
OL,12,Fsays: "We see a complete connection
OL,13,Fbetween the price increases and people
OL,14,Fusing the postal service year, so it
OL,15,Fis a worry.
OL,17,F"It's something that we're really
OL,18,Fproactive about as a card company - we
OL,19,Fhave to make it easy and affordable".
