OL,6,FLast week, they launched a second
OL,7,Fclass option to their card deals which
OL,8,Fhas proved successful.
OL,10,FThe price of postage has increased
OL,11,Facross both Bailiwicks in recent years:
OL,13,FAlison Baker, owner of Hallmark card
OL,14,Fshop in Jersey, has seen similar
OL,15,Ftrends since the pandemic.
OL,17,FShe says: "We've actually stopped
OL,18,Fselling stamps. We used to always sell
OL,19,Fstamps with our cards - but it got
OL,20,Fdifficult because they suddenly became
OL,21,Fso expensive last year.
