OL,6,F"It got embarrassing to sell a
OL,7,Fpostcard for 40p when the stamp would
OL,8,Fcost twice that.
OL,10,F"I think that has put people off -
OL,11,Fparticularly with sending cards to the
OL,12,Fmainland. People used to send 30, 40
OL,13,Fcards maybe - they just don't do that
OL,14,Fanymore."
OL,16,FOthers suggest that the tradition's
OL,17,Fdemise could also be associated with
OL,18,Fgenerational trends. Julie Thomas,
OL,19,FManaging Director at Jersey Post, says
OL,20,Fthey've witnessed "a younger person
OL,21,Fbias".
