OL,6,FShe says: "Young people are not
OL,7,Fbothered if they don't receive a card.
OL,8,FThey see writing cards as pointless,
OL,9,Fthey can stay in touch in other ways
OL,10,Fwith social media."
OL,12,F"But even the older generation are
OL,13,Fgetting to the point where they have
OL,14,Freduced the number of people they are
OL,15,Fsending cards to."
OL,17,FHowever, Julie adds a message of hope:
OL,18,Fan area that's not in decline is
OL,19,Fletters written to Father Christmas.
