OL,6,FShe says: "Year in, year out, we send
OL,7,F1500 letters to the North Pole - and
OL,8,Fthat number is not in decline.
OL,10,F"And each and every one of those
OL,11,Fchildren who writes to Santa Claus
OL,12,Fwill get a reply."
